{"id":189004,"type":2,"name":"激走！ルーベンカイザー","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/22/6f/189004_9MSDK.jpg","summary":"F1ドライバーの速水俊介は日本グランプリのレース中、監督からの指示を無視してマシンをクラッシュさせてしまい、レース後にチームから解雇されてしまう。そこへ、俊介の父の旧友で「カイザー・チーム」の監督を務める嵐銀二郎が現れた。銀二郎は俊介の腕を見込みチームのドライバーとして加入させた。カイザー・チームが誇る高性能フォーミュラカー「ルーベンカイザー・フォーミュラー1」は、実は俊介の父であるゲオルグ・カイザー設計のマシンだった。俊介は亡き父の夢をかなえるべく、このマシンで世界を目指す。","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>17</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1977-10-10</li><li><span>播放结束: </span>1978-2-6</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"on_hold":2,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"1977年10月","count":1},{"name":"1977年十月番","count":1},{"name":"1977年","count":1},{"name":"1977","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":653848,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653848","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653849,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653849","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653850,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653850","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653851,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653851","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653852,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653852","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653853,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653853","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653854,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653854","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653855,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653855","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":653856,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/653856","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","commen